data.title: The Saw Doctors – Official Website of The Saw Doctors
data.text:
UK Shows | Winter 2024

New Single – ‘Man in the Moon‘

The Saw Doctors will release a new single ‘Man in the Moon’ on Friday May 24 on Spotify and all the

streaming platforms. ‘Man in the Moon’ was written by Davy Carton, Leo Moran and Padraig Stevens.

The new single was recorded at Grouse Lodge Studios in Ireland with producer Philip Tennant.

Belfast Custom House Square | Sat 24th August

The Saw Doctors will play a summer gig in Belfast on Saturday 24th August. The outdoor show will

take place at Custom House Square in the centre of Belfast. Special Guests are The Undertones.

A Pre Sale of Belfast tickets, exclusively for Saw Doctors fans, will start this Thursday at 9am.
